Package: claude-voice-server
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: redrum
Installed-Size: 48
Depends: python3, python3-flask
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jerimie81/claude-voice-integration-apk
Description: PC-side relay server for Claude Voice Android app
 Flask HTTP server that receives voice queries from the Claude Voice Android
 app, forwards them to the Claude CLI, and streams responses back via SSE.
 .
 Components:
  - /opt/claude-voice-server/claude_webhook_server.py : Flask relay server
  - /opt/claude-voice-server/run-server.sh            : startup wrapper
  - /usr/lib/systemd/user/claude-voice-server.service : user systemd unit
